STATE OF CONNECTICUT v. FREDERICK WARREN (13793)

Schaller, Spear and Hennessy, Js.

Argued September 18 decision released October 10, 1995 Jeffrey D. Hutcoe, for the appellant (defendant). *903Denise B. Smoker, deputy assistant state’s attorney, with whom, on the brief, were James E. Thomas, state’s attorney, and Anne Mahoney, deputy assistant state’s attorney, for the appellee (state). PER CURIAM.
